name: Nobody Home
description:
I have a sad Joke,
walking while embracing the Pain.
unforgettable memories,
become a Parasite when you remember.
Eyes looking to the North,
I smile a color appears with Laughter.
-
the patter of Dreams,
reaches the conscience.
Sobs, Shortness of breath, Shattered dreams.
the roar of worry is only an inch from consciousness.
Then sign Painfully,
that the body longs to touch happiness to return to the World game.
-
Loss is nothing compared to memories,
because the Pain is much deeper and sticks in the memory.
